          },
          {
            "articleText": "article__text--second",
            "text": "This site presents my user experience projects."
          },
          {
            "articleText": "article__text--second",
            "text": "When creating websites, it is crucial to define the user and his needs, capabilities, functionality and design the website so as to best suit the product."
          },
          {
            "articleText": "article__text--second",
            "text": "In 2019 I did the 'UX design' course of InfoShare Academy, led by Karolina Troka (PGS Software S.A.), which allowed me to carry out this process better. In 2020, I also participated in the UX design workshops for the 'Żeton' application project, led by Weronik Spaleniak (Digital Toucan: Panorama & JQL Search Extensions for Jira)."
          },
