            "text": "'Zielone Słodzone' - online home patisserie"
          },
          {
            "articleText": "article__text--second",
            "text": "In 2020, I designed a website for a micro home patisserie. Brief UX helped me recognise the client's needs, and 'screener' and 'persona' helped me identify the specifics of potential customers. The client offered only two products, so the entire offer could be presented on the landing page. The site was to be ultimately connected to the blog that the client intended to create. I prepared the prototype in InVision."
