            "sectionTitle": "section__title--second",
            "text": "Redesigning of SkyCash"
          },
          {
            "articleText": "article__text--second",
            "text": "During the 'UX Designer' course, our team carried out a project to improve the smoothness of operations in the application on the example of the SkyCash application. The team included: Paweł Nieczuja-Ostrowski, Marta Gołyszyn, Krzysztof Osiak, Sylwia Tokarska, and Magdalena Mańko."
          },
          {
            "articleText": "article__text--second",
            "text": "To thoroughly understand the needs and problems of users we have created a questionnaire. Then we carried out: 1) direct research combined with in-depth interview, regarding behavior, 2) field research, using the appropriate tool (application) to register the ticket purchase process."
          },
          {
            "articleText": "article__text--second",
            "text": "In the research, we used a program recording the operation of purchasing tickets on the phone and an application for quick assessment of purchase satisfaction by the respondent - created especially for this task by me - which I called SkyFace. We developed the prototype in Figma program, and its final version was made by Krzysztof Osiak."
          },
          {
